n your 2026 vehicle with EYE TRACKING and extra spy bullshit installed for 2026 watches everything. The flock cameras watch everything. The intersection cameras watch everything. Then you use your credit card to do the final payment (sorry no cash allowed) for your final tracking data point.</p>\n<p>But TV and movies is a key component of all of that happening. At home and medicated with an empty head.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 5, "score_up": 16, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBvQQb2t", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 28, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "melania", "id": 8739447, "raw_content": "", "author": "kek-is-tan", "created": 1784607449173, "profile_picture": "I8XXB1DBtIOB", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "kek-is-tan", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBvQQb2t.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/It6uzyzvlsun.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/n0Lgyn0uFILYQxry.png", "width": 594, "content-type": "png", "height": 740}], "blurhash": "UNOgB4JQ~Vs=00OEs:n%4TNx9GjDIVWAxuof", "full_resolution": [740, 594]}, "title": "F*ck him and his goofy sister. \ud83d\udd95\ud83c\udffc\ud83d\udd95\ud83c\udffc", "last_comment_created": 1784607658705, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 4, "score_up": 28, "is_edited": false, 